Marcus B. HARRIS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
William F. CRENSHAW, CEO of Publix Supermarkets, Inc., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-5081 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 26, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of certiorari and supplemental petition for writ of certiorari are denied.

NORTHCUTT, MORRIS, and BLACK, JJ., Concur.
